# Cloud Run env vars reference (YAML)
# This project uses Secret Manager for env vars (see Cloud Run → ynm-website → Variables & Secrets).
# To add or update via file instead:
#   1. Copy to .env.gcp.yaml and fill values (do not commit .env.gcp.yaml).
#   2. gcloud run services update ynm-website --env-vars-file .env.gcp.yaml --region asia-south1 --project YOUR_GCP_PROJECT_ID
#
# Required (all forms + chatbot + careers):
#   GOOGLE_SHEET_ID, GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_EMAIL, GOOGLE_PRIVATE_KEY,
#   GOOGLE_GEMINI_API_KEY, GMAIL_USER, GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD, HR_EMAIL,
#   CAREERS_NOREPLY_FROM
#
# Optional:
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID,
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY
#
# Google Sheet must have 5 tabs: "contact us", "our director appointment",
# "investor relations", "foreign collaborations", "quote requests"
